long_description: if you're traveling for leisure or work, feel free to relax in our passenger lounge while you await take-off. skywerx aviation is a premier fbo headquartered at the blair municipal airport, only 20 minutes from the omaha area business centers. we provide affordable flying services, management, and aircraft acquisition. we are up front and personal with all of our clients.
